➤ Tune into Amazing Facts Radio - https://www.amazingfacts.org/media-library/listen
➤ Amazing Facts of Faith Archives - https://www.amazingfacts.org/media-library/watch/archives/o/154/t/amazing-facts-of-faith

What is it that people find so enchanting about lions? Is it their speed, their claws, their sharp teeth—or all of the above? Pastor Doug explores the mighty “king of beasts,” delving into some fascinating “man-eating” and "vegetable-eating" stories from history that will amaze you!

And did you know the Bible mentions lions more than 100 times? Indeed, they have major significance as symbols in the Bible. Learn more is this insightful, inspirational, and fascinating "Amazing Facts of Faith."
